quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,46,"Aŵala ŵaakusimichisya kuti tachisimangana ni M’mbuje gwao (Allah), soni kuti ŵanganyao Kukwakwe chachiujila."
  2,47,"E jenumanja ŵanache ŵa Israila! Kumbuchilani chindimba Changu chanampele, soni nanchimbichisye kupunda iwumbe yosope (ya ndaŵi jenu)."
  2,48,"Ni lijogopani Lisiku lyangakomboleka mundu kunkamuchisya mundu jwine chilichose, soni ngasikukundidwa kutyochela kwa jwalakwejo kuchondelela, atamuno chaliwombolela chakuuma kukwakwe ngasichipocheledwa, soni ŵanganyao ngasaŵa ŵakulupusyidwa."